{"tid":1071045,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"日日行都錯？穿梭巴逆線行幾十米　司機急停","createTime":"2019-03-21T05:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T06:28:18.000Z","uid":225464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"03284fbe7ebdcc9d26643dea91e9f2ee1a6f4b54","tid":1071045,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>日日行都錯？穿梭巴逆線行幾十米 司機急停</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2FhkHSU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FhkHSU&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3PolgVFqTZkzW3om5iGclzM%3D&h=9a9ffebd\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2FhkHSU</a><br />\n（<span style=\"color: red;\">Shorten link同網賺link都唔識分嘅on9仔自己去google吓</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190321/photo/bkn-20190321114449168-0321_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190321122538\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190321%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190321114449168-0321_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190321122538&h=ebdbf50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔熟路定未瞓醒？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日復日行駛同一路徑都會出錯？近日就有失魂司機駕駛穿梭巴士時不慎轉入鄰線，逆線而行，惹來網民質疑︰「這是正式錄用的司機嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n片段被上傳至Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」，只見星期四（21日）上午8時許，有一架機場快綫穿梭巴士在九龍佐敦道的十字路口，準備右轉至匯民道。<br />\n<br />\n未料穿梭巴士竟轉彎駛入鄰線，反方向直行。司機疑驚覺自己走錯路，欲於柯士甸站附近掉頭折返。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民直呼離譜︰「冇資格揸巴士，會累死人」、「日日行同一條路都可以錯？」、「1823嚴懲這類馬路炸彈，否則只會後患無窮」。有人不禁揶揄司機︰「幫佢解釋吓先，可能第一次行呢條線」。"},{"pid":"123d91c9901f606efe2f2bf86c4c2d1cd0fa3f04","tid":1071045,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190321/photo/bkn-20190321114449168-0321_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190321122538\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190321%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190321114449168-0321_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190321122538&h=b3c55c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍色的機場快綫穿梭巴士轉彎駛入鄰線。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"1a2aafab0ffb32dad8cec698019d6ac29e26548f","tid":1071045,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190321/photo/bkn-20190321114449168-0321_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190321122538\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190321%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190321114449168-0321_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190321122538&h=32e03901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n司機疑驚覺走錯路隨即掉頭（箭嘴示）。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"79754ce5b4670feec72752ad724bdc296a1f4206","tid":1071045,"uid":71133,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"西九大角嘴堆新路係好撚on9，成日都驚自己入錯逆線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過日日揸都錯另計"},{"pid":"69674e422fe353a0e8afd32b09722e3aebca33df","tid":1071045,"uid":66242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"79754ce5b4670feec72752ad724bdc296a1f4206","tid":1071045,"uid":71133,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"西九大角嘴堆新路係好撚on9，成日都驚自己入錯逆線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過日日揸都錯另計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:28:18.000Z","msg":"路面係闊<br />\n但係連翔道啲匯入匯出線交匯處好混亂<br />\n路牌混亂<br />\n俾駕駛者反應嘅距離唔夠<br />\n令到睇路好眼花<br />\n由西隧出嚟入尖山<br />\n我唔係上咗去大角咀迴旋處就去咗貨櫃碼頭<br />\n<br />\n另外櫻桃街嗰度有個連四五個燈位嘅超大迴旋處<br />\n又唔順燈<br />\n如果走漏一個路口無出到再兜個圈<br />\n要搞成幾分鐘先出到個無間輪迴<br />\n搞到路面一截截"}]}